PhotoVault is a professional App for you to secures photos. This app will NEVER upload your photos to the cloud. And also the local data saved in your device are encrypted by AES. So there is no way to access your photos without your passcode.

Main features:

- Face ID && Touch ID;
- Custom albums;
- Manage photos in album easily;
- Import && export with just one click;
- Beautiful design and easy to use;
- Full-screen viewing photos;
- Local data encrypted;
- Ads free;

More features are coming.

